title: Donarr the Unyielding (2013) (digital) (d'argh-Empire).cbr
description:
Donarr the Unyielding (2013) (digital) (d'argh-Empire)


In 2012 an alien prison ship uprising has freed thousands. While the guardians of the universe, the Peacekeepers, fight for control of the spacecraft, it crashes into Earth's atmosphere causing a mass extinction! Flash forward a millennium. A shattered world, where humans struggle to survive against the alien outlaws, exists. Their only hope is the last Peacekeeper - Donarr the Unyielding!
